&lt;li&gt;Experience with C++ 11/14/17/20, Linux and Python and BASH scripting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-depth knowledge of the Linux kernel, systems programming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for solving challenging problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong systems knowledge and prefer some experience in developing low latency systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with writing applications connecting to exchange API’s or using network protocols&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with parallel, concurrent, and multi-threaded programming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prefer experience with low-latency computing and hardware-level design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Git, SVN, Mercurial&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
