&lt;li&gt;Proficient in derivatives and volatility modeling, including the construction and calibration of forward curves and volatility surfaces. Possess extensive knowledge of equity and index derivative products, including variance derivatives, VIX, and other related instruments. Experience with dividend swaps and futures is considered advantageous.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have programming skills in Python and C++ are a prerequisite&lt;/li&gt;
