&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Knowledge of European ETF market&lt;br&gt;• Prior experience in a trading operations role required&lt;br&gt;• Proficient in Python, SQL, and&amp;nbsp;Excel (including VBA)&lt;br&gt;• Familiarity with Linux a plus&lt;br&gt;• Excellent problem-solving and critical thinking skills&lt;br&gt;• Strong attention to detail&lt;br&gt;• Experience working within a global team&lt;/p&gt;
